                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/850" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0077</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9832 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“七年之痒”——长城钻探在A国本地员工的人力资源管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王雪莉，路峭等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">清华大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油集团长城钻探工程有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长城钻探；跨文化人力资源管理；文化差异；员工本地化；中国企业国际化；2012百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Great Wall Drilling Company; Cross-cultural human resource management; Cultural differences; Personnel localization; The internationalization of Chinese enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">      长城钻探是中国石油旗下的专业化石油工程技术服务公司，近年来公司海外项目的主要技术和管理人员从中方派遣，发挥了人才优势并快速抢占市场。随着海外市场不断扩大，人力资源短缺、人工成本攀升、东道国使用当地人员限制、外派人员安全风险增加、跨文化冲突等问题日益严峻，人力资源问题逐步成为制约公司发展的瓶颈。为实现总承包商目标，公司加快发展海外市场，实行人员本地化是国际化发展的必然选择，但是由于国情和企业性质的不同，缺乏跨文化管理的人才、经验和资源，公司希望找到更为完善的本地化人力资源管理策略。
    本案例适合于MBA、研究生、本科生以及企业管理人员在《跨文化人力资源管理》课程上讨论使用。本案例描述了公司背景、东道国概况、气测人员本地化现状、竞争对手、面临的挑战及未来等方面内容。通过使用本案例，学生可以将人力资源管理的理论与企业实践相结合，更好地理解相关知识，思考跨文化人力资源管理中文化差异、属地人员管理、外派管理人员的甄选和培训等方面的关键点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">    The Great Wall Drilling Company, as a subsidiary of the PetroChina, is focused on providing professional petroleum engineering technology services. During past years, it has quickly seized the oversea market by sending out principal technical and managerial personnel to implement its overseas projects. However, with the expanding overseas markets, this company’s further development has encountered a series of human resource bottlenecks, such as human resources shortages, rising labor costs, the using restrictions of the host country’s personnel, safety risks increasing of expatriates, cross-cultural conflict, etc. In order to achieve the goal of being a general contractor, it is an inevitable choice of internationalization that the company has to keep accelerating its development in overseas markets and the implementation of personnel localization, while due to the different national conditions and the corporate nature, as well as its lack of experience and resources of the cross-cultural management, the company is willing to find better management strategy of the human resource localization.
    This case is prepared for class discussions of MBA students, graduate students, undergraduate students, or business managers in the course of “cross-cultural human resource management”. With vast information of the company’s background, the host country’s profile, localization situation of the gas logging personnel, and the company’s business competitors,  potential challenges and its future perspective, etc., students can combine the human resource management theory with the company’s business practice for a better understanding of the relevant knowledge, and to think about a few key points about the cultural differences in cross-cultural human resource management, the local personnel management, and the expatriate managers’ selection and training, etc.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《跨文化人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨文化人力资源管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-09</td>
                            </tr>
